        "content": "<p>Dataverse sends the server IP instead of domain name as redirect_uri when logging in through OpenID. Is it possible to change this behaviour?</p>",
        "id": 429319102,
        "sender_full_name": "Mohsen Jafari",
        "timestamp": 1711356546
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"698782\">Mohsen Jafari</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/378866-troubleshooting/topic/Sending.20domain.20name.20instead.20of.20IP.20when.20using.20OpenID/near/429319102\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Dataverse sends the server IP instead of domain name as redirect_uri when logging in through OpenID. Is it possible to change this behaviour?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Hello, take a look at the dataverse.siteUrl and dataverse.fqdn jvm-options?</p>",
